Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:03.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:10.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail wizards!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:14.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.29,0:00:16.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nichiya-san, are they...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.80,0:00:20.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:57.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:01:59.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oyoyoyoyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:02.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna save everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:06.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna save 'em, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.97,0:02:10.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nichiya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:16.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Angels who have lost their \Nwings... The Fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:21.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Exceeds have been poisoned by the \Nfilth of Earthland and have Fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:25.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:28.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two of the Fallen are escaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:30.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Royal Guard, go forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:35.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly! To Your Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:47.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that Happy's a traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:50.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way in hell, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:52.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:56.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Open this cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:57.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:59.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bust this thing wide open!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:03.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:08.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:14.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Edolas is so damn annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:15.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:26.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.13,0:03:28.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:31.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! This has got to be \Nsome sort of joke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:36.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right... Everyone was captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu... Happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy... Carla...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:44.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did everyone go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:47.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And hey... Let me outta these!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:49.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can anybody hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:50.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,God, she's loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:03:59.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's a caterpillar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:03.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obviously not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:06.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's coming from the castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:08.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't those...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:11.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:19.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's those heroes from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:22.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And... the Royal Guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:27.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:31.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:43.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:47.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not tired, or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:49.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still young!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:53.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I must live up to the Queen's expectations!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:18.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:23.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on real tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:24.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:49.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Carla... Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:51.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:57.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:00.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That lacrima is floating!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:03.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's way bigger than the one \Nwe saw in the Royal City.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:05.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's everyone from Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:08.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's where they were...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:11.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:18.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we on a floating island?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:21.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Royal City is way down there, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:24.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, the situation \Nwould look like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:27.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How are we going to get \Ndown to the Royal City?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:32.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't use our Aera like we are now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:36.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:40.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:42.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck ya think \Nyer doin' on my fields?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:44.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:52.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer those Fallen who the Royal Guard \N're searchin' about for, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:05.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye! We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.39,0:07:07.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:12.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did that cart which ran me \Nover head over this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:15.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Search for it, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:16.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're already after us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said get outta my fields!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:26.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye! We'll leave right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:27.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then come to my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the soldiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:38.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you already report to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:46.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My, you're home early today, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:49.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:52.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:56.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:01.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. What lovely names!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:03.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, please come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:18.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my... That sounds like \Nquite a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:24.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, ma'am... Thank you for sheltering us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:27.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat yer food, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:28.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:30.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:35.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My husband here doesn't really \Ngo with how the kingdom thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:40.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were kicked out long ago, \Nand make our lives here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:43.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go blabbin' about that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:44.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:47.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So that's why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:53.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After you eat, yer gonna help with the work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:58.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Put this on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:00.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:09.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Put yer back in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:11.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You call yerself a man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:15.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never done this before...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:17.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:20.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it faster! Put yer back in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:21.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.55,0:09:30.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that a hoe \Nwas this heavy, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:32.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:37.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here, you... That's called \Nthe weight of life itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:39.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:42.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure makes a big deal outta things...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:45.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if he hears me, he'll get \Nmad, so I'll keep it to myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:48.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:51.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:58.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:00.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If yer a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:03.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Put some back into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:12.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doin' this much is just par for the course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:14.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're pretty amazing, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just gawk at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:20.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was just gawking at it himself... \NOr did he forget already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:24.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if he hears me, he'll get \Nmad, so I'll keep it to myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:26.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told ya, I can hear it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:29.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:34.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're very good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:35.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:36.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:38.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:44.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You weak-kneed little...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:46.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:55.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No more...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:57.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Weakling...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:11:01.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've made some nice cold drinks! \NWhy don't you rest for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:02.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:06.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go drinkin' before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:07.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:29.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad they let me out of those stocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:32.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but what's with this sticky stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:34.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:36.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd really appreciate you taking \Noff this sticky stuff, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I can escape anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:39.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:41.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,God, she's loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:45.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are all Earthland women like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:50.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sensing any magical \Npower from my keys...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.01,0:11:54.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, this sticky stuff \Nis suppressing my magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:58.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:13.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work on your mission. Hurry \Nup and take me back to the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:19.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I took them to the Royal \NCity, just like you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:23.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys are seriously planning \Non taking on the Royal Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:26.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:29.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you refill this thing's lacrima?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:35.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The army has searched through the \Nblack market and everywhere else,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:37.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and there isn't even a \Nshard of a lacrima left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:41.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll be out of magic power \Nabout when we reach the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:46.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet you had me ride to \Nthe Royal City and back...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:47.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:51.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're such big softies, you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:56.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get all cheeky with me, bub!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:58.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:02.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Technique #31: Studly Bomber!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:09.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy that he's hiding us, \Nbut he sure works me hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, {\i1}sorry{\i0} for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:13.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No complainin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:14.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:16.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured he could hear me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Natsu and the others are safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:25.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't have time \Nto be doing this stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:33.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go thinkin' of other \Nstuff when yer workin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:34.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:37.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After yer done with that, \Nwe'll be splittin' logs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:39.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:49.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't smiled once since you \Ncame to this house, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:52.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you have such a pretty face...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:56.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am in no mood to smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:14:00.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're struggling with something, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:04.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's even more important to \Nsmile during those times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:06.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:10.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,True... It's not so simple, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:18.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:20.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:22.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You call that log-splittin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:31.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I ain't gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:34.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir! Aye, sir! Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:37.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't losin' neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:40.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How competitive are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:42.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Same to ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:44.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the last log!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:46.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:48.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll split it first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:00.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:01.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:05.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, fine. We'll leave it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:09.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go take a bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:12.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:23.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:31.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you leave me alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:32.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:34.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:38.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me "because"... \NGo home by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.19,0:15:42.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:46.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:49.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:52.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:58.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That bath felt incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:05.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, Carla... What exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:10.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:16.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it feel nice here \Nafter taking a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.54,0:16:18.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, very much so!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:21.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your names are Happy and Carla, if I recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:23.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were born on Earthland, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:26.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it that named you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:29.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu. My friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:32.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The same for me... A friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:36.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those friends have been \Ncaptured by the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:39.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:41.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're going to rescue humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:46.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In Extalia, thinking like that is wrong, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:50.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the case. I think it's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:55.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Being friends has nothing to do \Nwith being Human or Exceed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:17:02.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, even if we look different, the \Nshape of your heart that loves others is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The shape of your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:09.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The shape of a loving heart \Nis the same for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:16.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:23.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart isn't my own... It's being \Nmanipulated by someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:29.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know if the words \NI'm saying now are my own, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:33.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're your words, Carla! \NIt's your heart, Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:40.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our hearts that want to rescue \Nour friends are our own!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:42.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:48.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right. You might be a little \Nlost now, but I'm sure you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:51.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have such a wonderful \Nknight next to you, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:54.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Knight-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:58.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can find your own heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:01.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, it's already within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:10.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All you need to do is realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:14.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in the love you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:25.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness... You finally smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:27.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:28.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a strange one, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:30.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:35.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because all the Exceeds think that \Nthey're like angels or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:38.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that humans are an inferior race.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:42.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I once thought like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:46.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But then our children were \Ntaken by the Queen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:55.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She collected eggs... 100 children, for \Nthe Dragon Slayer Extermination Project.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:19:03.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, without even seeing the faces of our \Nchildren, they were sent to Earthland.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:10.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were kicked out of the kingdom \Nbecause we opposed the project...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:12.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was around that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:16.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't gods or angels...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:21.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just parents, that's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:23.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:30.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it didn't matter whether one \Nwas an Exceed or a Human any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:36.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My husband can be a bit harsh, \Nbut I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:41.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talkin' about that dumb stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:43.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer are y'gonna be here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:44.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:47.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer makin' such a down face!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:49.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just livin' is happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a softy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:56.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear, isn't that a bit sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.47,0:20:00.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:04.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go save everyone, and soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:06.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:10.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay bein' this scared, you \Ncouldn't do it even if you had a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:13.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids these days don't understand nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:24.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, sir! Thanks, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:27.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never darken my door again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:29.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:36.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla, did you understand what he just said?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:38.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:42.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I arrived at Edolas, \NI was filled with unease!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:44.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... As was I.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:47.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But things are different now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:58.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to move forward! We have to fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:07.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're Exceeds... The only creatures in \NEdolas who have magic power inside them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:11.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason we couldn't use magic was \Nbecause of the unease in our hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:25.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See? When we can see the shape of our \Nhearts, wings will let us move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:29.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! We have to save everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:30.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:36.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look a that, Marl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:38.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They {\i1}can{\i0} fly after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:42.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He flies just like you, Lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.10,0:21:45.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! It ain't \Njust in how he {\i1}flies{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:47.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:08.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that she was his girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.19,0:22:14.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer 100 years too young to \Nbe bringin' a girl home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.36,0:22:17.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was raised to be a kind child \Nwho's thoughtful of his friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:21.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.95,0:24:00.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to save you, Natsu! That's \Nlike opposite the usual pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.62,0:24:01.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.45,0:24:03.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, I'm all excited though!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.55,0:24:06.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to think of myself as the \Nmain character this time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.43,0:24:08.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, just come save us already!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.17,0:24:12.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's this? Are you sure you \Nshould be talking to me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.39,0:24:14.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, your character's completely changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.10,0:24:16.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Code ETD!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.78,0:24:20.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's less like being the hero, \Nand more being the big evil boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.01,0:24:23.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The big evil boss, huh? I think I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.14,0:24:25.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now {\i1}you{\i0} need help...
